Text.val: Jumps to the proper field. This needs to be manually set due to different visible conditions on controls.
Otherwise, when moving between the lines of different var types, the focus jumps from a 'From' var to a 'To' var.

ExpSyntax.val: 'Locate cannot be defined on the same field twice.'

CtrlGoto( CASE({0,7},'A','AlpUni','U','AlpUni','N','Num','D','Date','T','Time','L','Logical','') & IF (LastPark(0)='' OR InStr(LastPark(0),'From')>0,'From','') & IF (InStr(LastPark(0),'To')>0,'To','') & IF ({0,35} AND ({0,7}='A' OR {0,7}='U' OR {0,7}='N'),'Combo','') ,0,0)
